She lookd at Rex, "Are all Maximals like you? Or do some of you 
actually loosen up and relax? I mean, You look so uptight, you look 
like your about to bust a gear." she said with a laugh.
"You can relax you know.  Oh and smiling once in a while wouldn't 
hurt either." she said with a chuckle.

She was determended to win the maximals over. She would need al the 
support she could get if she was to be successful and get the leader 
to go with her to the talks.  One she knew for sure about maximal, 
when the soldiers agreed on something, the leaders would usually go 
along.  She hoped it was working.  She still ahdn't talked to the 
leader yet and it was getting frustrating for her.  She hoped 
Cybershark was having better luck than her.
